<plot>'Arthur's Lore' is a fantasy action comedy that updates the Legend of King Arthur to modern day. ARTHUR is enjoying a drink in the pub with his girlfriend, GWYNN, and his friends LANCE and MERYL, when a fateful stabbing changes his life forever. Suddenly he's the Saviour of Britain, an ancient king reincarnated to fight the BANSHEES - beautiful yet deadly wraiths who steal your soul with their terrible cry. Luckily, Arthur is not alone in this fight. He's aided by his wisecracking mates, feisty chav princess Gwynn and the mysterious Lady in the Bath.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?046661</url></doc>
